we are dealing with a moment

00:13:07.840 --> 00:13:16.940
where anti-black criminalization
is being pumped up

00:13:16.940 --> 00:13:18.640
by media coverage.

00:13:18.640 --> 00:13:21.460
It's being sustained
by media coverage.

00:13:21.460 --> 00:13:24.460
And I think that these
outlets have a responsibility

00:13:24.460 --> 00:13:29.560
to be very clear that the
police narrative is not

00:13:29.560 --> 00:13:31.380
the official story.

00:13:31.380 --> 00:13:33.070
Let me just say this.

00:13:33.070 --> 00:13:37.940
The title, the headline when the
woman was killed in Seattle--

00:13:37.940 --> 00:13:38.830
so yesterday.

00:13:38.830 --> 00:13:42.760
