of the first police

00:15:48.630 --> 00:15:50.650
officers in this country were--

00:15:50.650 --> 00:15:55.000
their job was to catch
runaway slaves and to patrol.

00:15:55.000 --> 00:15:59.660
Their purpose was largely
to capture runaway slaves

00:15:59.660 --> 00:16:01.000
and patrol for runaway slaves.

00:16:04.030 --> 00:16:08.620
Early legal precedent
dictated that a black man

00:16:08.620 --> 00:16:10.990
has no rights a white
man is bound to respect.

00:16:10.990 --> 00:16:16.540
All of these legal
standards have

00:16:16.540 --> 00:16:19.110
been baked into how we
think about and deal

00:16:19.110 --> 00:16:21.520
with policing in this country.

00:16:21.520 --> 00:16:23.480
And so when you
ask this question,

00:16:23.480 --> 00:16:30.700
what can be done to extract or
to add pressure to the system?

00:16:30.700 --> 00:16:34.390
Number one, there's an
entire legal strategy at work

00:16:34.390 --> 00:16:38.477
that folks are using, both
in terms of trying to--

00:16:41.110 --> 00:16:45.280
so there are lots of
places where lawyers are

00:16:45.280 --> 00:16:47.320
trying to attack the system.

00:16:47.320 --> 00:16:48.994
One of the places
that organizers

00:16:48.994 --> 00:16:50.410
are trying to
attack the system is

00:16:50.410 --> 00:16:54.080
by changing who our prosecutors
are in different cities

00:16:54.080 --> 00:16:55.400
and states.

00:16:55.400 --> 00:16:58.210
So there's been an entire
campaign by Color of Change

00:16:58.210 --> 00:17:02.340
to transform the face
of prosecutors and DAs

00:17:02.340 --> 00:17:03.422
in this country.

00:17:03.422 --> 00:17:05.810
I think that's one way, right?

00:17:05.810 --> 00:17:08.650
But we also see that in
Baltimore, when a district

00:17:08.650 --> 00:17:14.319
attorney tried to actually
convict some officers,

00:17:14.319 --> 00:17:17.410
not only did that
not happen, but she

00:17:17.410 --> 00:17:21.890
was completely outcasted and
also made into a criminal.

00:17:21.890 --> 00:17:24.849
She faced criminal charges,
because that's what

00:17:24.849 --> 00:17:26.630
the system is set up to do.

00:17:26.630 --> 00:17:28.060
And it's not set up--

00:17:28.060 --> 00:17:29.670
so when we talk
about police reform,

00:17:29.670 --> 00:17:33.580
when we talk about, for
example, body-worn cameras,

00:17:33.580 --> 00:17:37.330
this is one place where there's,
I think, a false solution being

00:17:37.330 --> 00:17:40.420
offered, where you're
offering to people

00:17:40.420 --> 00:17:47.160
this opportunity to
record, but that does not

00:17:47.160 --> 00:17:48.550
invest any change.

00:17:48.550 --> 00:17:52.320
There's no change
involved in that.

00:17:52.320 --> 00:17:54.560
These piecemeal
reforms are not going

00:17:54.560 --> 00:17:58.060
to make it so that police
don't kill black people.

00:17:58.060 --> 00:17:59.901
The only thing that
will make it so police

00:17:59.901 --> 00:18:01.400
don't kill black
people is if we are

00:18:01.400 --> 00:18:07.600
able to abolish policing
as we currently know it

00:18:07.600 --> 00:18:10.060
and rebuild it
into something that

00:18:10.060 --> 00:18:12.280
actually has a new
form of security,

00:18:12.280 --> 00:18:13.660
new forms of accountability.

00:18:13.660 --> 00:18:17.230
That's the only thing that
I think is going to work.

00:18:17.230 --> 00:18:22.000
We can attack-- we can run
our various legal strategies.

00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:24.070
We can make piecemeal reforms.

00:18:24.070 --> 00:18:24.960
But we can see--

00:18:24.960 --> 00:18:26.490
right now, the
Justice Department

00:18:26.490 --> 00:18:28.690
is actively rolling
back any reforms

00:18:28.690 --> 00:18:32.480
that have been moved forward Any
consent decrees, any of that.

00:18:32.480 --> 00:18:34.870
So in reality, what
we know is this--

00:18:34.870 --> 00:18:37.190
it's a question of power.

00:18:37.190 --> 00:18:40.810
Who has the power will
determine what the results are.

00:18:40.810 --> 00:18:44.650
And two, these piecemeal
reforms, they just don't work.

00:18:44.650 --> 00:18:47.260
We've been trying them
for hundreds of years.

00:18:47.260 --> 00:18:49.574
They do not work.

