00:19:28.500 --> 00:19:30.130
So net neutrality is
certainly an issue

00:19:30.130 --> 00:19:36.310
that we are in the thick of
as Google, as an internet

00:19:36.310 --> 00:19:38.325
content company.

00:19:38.325 --> 00:19:40.450
But this notion of net
neutrality as a civil rights

00:19:40.450 --> 00:19:40.950
issue.

00:19:40.950 --> 00:19:42.089
What do you mean by that?

00:19:42.089 --> 00:19:43.630
MALKIA CYRIL: Well,
