or not police can shoot and kill

00:19:50.356 --> 00:19:51.770
us with impunity.

00:19:51.770 --> 00:19:53.530
Here's the reality.

00:19:53.530 --> 00:19:58.510
I don't care about Netflix
versus Comcast versus--

00:19:58.510 --> 00:20:01.069
I don't care about
these big companies.

00:20:01.069 --> 00:20:02.110
You know what I'm saying?

00:20:02.110 --> 00:20:03.220
I honestly don't.

00:20:03.220 --> 00:20:06.100
What I care about
is Philando Castile.

00:20:06.100 --> 00:20:08.040
I care about whether
or not you'll

00:20:08.040 --> 00:20:14.890
be able to see this shooting and
have the spark of outrage that

00:20:14.890 --> 00:20:18.075
can turn into a wildfire
of protests, that can turn

00:20:18.075 --> 00:20:19.640
into a movement for change.

00:20:19.640 --> 00:20:22.990
Because the thing is that
without being able to see it,

00:20:22.990 --> 00:20:25.020
you can't do that.

00:20:25.020 --> 00:20:26.330
That's the bottom line.

00:20:26.330 --> 00:20:28.650
And for me, that's what net
neutrality is all about.

00:20:28.650 --> 00:20:29.525
You know what I mean?

00:20:29.525 --> 00:20:32.815
For some people, it's a
contest between major companies

00:20:32.815 --> 00:20:35.660
and who can get
the fastest access.

00:20:35.660 --> 00:20:39.210
There's a question around
what the market can bear

00:20:39.210 --> 00:20:40.585
and what it can't,
and regulating

00:20:40.585 --> 00:20:41.950
that and all of that.

00:20:41.950 --> 00:20:43.770
And that's for other
people to talk about.

00:20:43.770 --> 00:20:48.370
Somebody else can come and talk
to you about those specifics.

00:20:48.370 --> 00:20:49.450
I'm fine with that.

00:20:49.450 --> 00:20:52.450
For me, I only care
about net neutrality

00:20:52.450 --> 00:20:56.040
because it opens the
door for more mobility.

00:20:56.040 --> 00:20:58.930
It opens the door for black
people to speak freely.

00:20:58.930 --> 00:21:01.470
It opens the door
for us to bypass

00:21:01.470 --> 00:21:03.027
what I consider to be a--

00:21:03.027 --> 00:21:04.110
not what I consider to be.

00:21:04.110 --> 00:21:09.670
What facts tell us is a
white-dominated cable news

00:21:09.670 --> 00:21:11.110
media.

00:21:11.110 --> 00:21:13.360
You know, entertainment media.

00:21:13.360 --> 00:21:15.520
From entertainment
